long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Track time on tasks from your browser using this extension by integrating with the 3rd party platforms you use like JIRA, Trello, Asana, and more. The extension requires the latest version of Time Doctor desktop application to be installed.

How it works:

Admins: Video: https://support.timedoctor.com/knowledge/using-the-time-doctor-chrome-extension-for-company-owners/admins
 
Employees: Video: https://support.timedoctor.com/knowledge/using-the-time-doctor-chrome-extension-for-users
